f_{X+Y}(z)=\int_{\max(0,z-1)}^{\min(1,z)} f_X(x)f_Y(z-x)dx = \int_{\max(0,z-1)}^{\min(1,z)} 1 \, dx 
f_{X+Y}(z) = \begin{cases} z &\mbox{if } 0 \le z \le 1 \\ 2-z &\mbox{if } 1 \le z \le 2. \end{cases}  
P(X_1+X_2\le 2) = \int_0^2 f_{X+Y}(z)dz = \int_0^1 f_{X+Y}(z)dz + \int_1^2 f_{X+Y}(z)dz = \frac12+\frac12 =1
